  "design_notes": "A carefully paced medium chart with a clear peak structure. The intro starts with sparse quarter beats, picking up some 8th syncopation in the build. The first drop introduces lightweight stream patterns and brief holds mapping the lead melodies, while ensuring the density is broken up to stay within the 5.0 NPS limit. S4 offers a full breathing break with quarter beats before the second drop ramps up to peak energy, utilizing tight hold/tap coordination and light movement across the pad.",
